...
}
2. 程式碼與註解間應至少加上一個空格
3. System.out.println("length: "+ len);   --> System.out.println("length: " + len);
4. String sub = sentence.substring(28,35);  --> String sub = sentence.substring(28, 35);
     String replaced = sentence.replace("e","1");  --> String replaced = sentence.replace("e", "1");

你有初始化 enum value，所以 play 可以這樣寫：
if(user[i].getValue() != sysGesture[i].getValue()) {
                winCount += (user[i].getValue() > sysGesture[i].getValue() ? 1 : -1);
            }

for (int i = 0; i < railwayArray.length; i++) {
            Transportation railway;
            if (random.nextBoolean()) {
                System.out.print("Input train driver: ");
                String driver = scanner.next();
                System.out.print("Input train price: ");
                double price = scanner.nextInt();
                System.out.print("Input train road: ");
                double road = scanner.nextDouble();

                railway = new Train(driver,price,road);
            }
            else {
                System.out.print("Input taxi driver: ");
                String driver = scanner.next();
                System.out.print("Input taxi price: ");
                double price = scanner.nextInt();
                System.out.print("Input taxi way: ");
                int way = scanner.nextInt();

                railway = new Taxi(driver,price,way);

            }
            railwayArray[i] = railway;
        }
你的Train class 的price 的input 需是double型態，nextInt();=>nextDouble();

第49行：
average = (double)sum / 5;
在google check中，資料型態的轉換後需要空格
average = (double) sum / 5;

public ReadyMadeCake(String name, double rate, int quanity) {
    super(name, rate);
    this.quantity = quanity;
  }中的quanity應為quantity
